content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4607.26 - Supplier's gifts or donations prohibited

State Regulations

No licensed supplier, its duly authorized agent, salesperson or representative, shall furnish any equipment, devices or supplies
without a charge to a licensed organization; nor shall any agreement, oral or
written, be made to give or allow the use of any property or thing of value to
a licensed organization in consideration of its purchase, lease or use of the
licensed supplier's equipment, devices or supplies. Notes
